{"tid":1701973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[11.11] 黎明行動路面交通攻略","createTime":"2019-11-09T12:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T02:10:04.000Z","uid":108757,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c5bffa3ca794f6225cb0980e286000ae951ed3e1","tid":1701973,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:35:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uGFRhXE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuGFRhXE.jpg&h=6ec7e395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OM7HpCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOM7HpCF.jpg&h=4aac501b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港可以分為五部分︰新界西、新界東、西九龍、東九龍、港島 (離島唔計)<br />\n重點道路︰<br />\n1. 新界西 (屯元天)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屯門公路</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 新界東 (大埔沙田)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">吐露港公路</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 西九龍 (油尖旺)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">長沙灣道 + 彌敦道<br />\n窩打老道</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4. 東九龍 (九龍灣觀塘)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">龍翔道</span></span><br />\n<br />\n5. 港島 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三隧(唔洗過海)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n起碼<span style=\"color: red;\">七成</span>路面交通都係經以上道路，如果塞咗就好多人返唔到工。而且塞咗一條，其他分支路都會塞，到時<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全香港都返唔到工</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過你知我知，黑警都知。<br />\n大家記得早幾個鐘起身準備返工，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好遲到</span></span>！"},{"pid":"e587cf2e330ac837628e1b9dd6d5b12a651b974f","tid":1701973,"uid":244928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:37:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d38e4421dfa303b291c88890d433ef4f590701c6","tid":1701973,"uid":244928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor